                        <interp inst="t18370130-name-593" type="given" value="JAMES HENRY"></interp>JAMES HENRY ANDREWS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am an officer. I took the prisoner with the coat on—he said he lived at No. 7, North-street, Stepney—I went there, but could find nothing of him.</p>
